# Privacy Policy

**Effective Date:** August 31, 2025  
**XYRA LLC** ("we", "us", or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or interact with our services.

## Information We Collect
We may collect limited personal information such as:
- Wallet addresses (for funding and transaction purposes)
- Email addresses (if you contact us directly)
- Usage data (via analytics tools, if enabled)

We do **not** collect sensitive personal data, nor do we sell or share your information with third parties.

## How We Use Your Information
We use your information to:
- Facilitate wallet funding via MoonPay
- Improve site functionality and user experience
- Respond to inquiries or support requests

## Data Security
We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

## Third-Party Services
Our site may integrate with MoonPay or other crypto infrastructure providers. Their privacy policies apply when you interact with their services.

## Your Rights
You may request access to or deletion of your personal data by contacting us at: **xyra.llc@gmail.com**

## Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with a revised effective date.

## Contact
For questions or concerns, email us at: **xyra.llc@gmail.com**
